    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Could be cool to have a function that is able to generate an url from a \"state\".\n\nEx for magento: for now I need to do something like :\n\n```\n'#q=&page=0&refinements=%5B%7B%22categories%22%3A%5B%22'.$path.'%22%5D%7D%5D&numerics_refinements=%7B%7D&index_name=%22'.$indexName.'%22';\n```\n\nCould be cool to say something like:\n\n``` php\ngenerateUrl({\n 'refinements':<?php echo json_encode(['categories' => $path]); ?>,\n 'index_name': '<?php echo $indexName; ?>'\n}\n```\n",
